title: #92Noon Friday Feast!
description: It's the Friday football feast with PA & Charch! Super Stats Dave calls in to break down a potential scenario where the Timberwolves wind up with 2 first round picks.  Chad Greenway joins the show for his weekly segment to talk Mike Zimmer's contract negotiations.  Plus, plenty of NFL conversation between PA & Charch!
